survey_response.review_text:
I am 47 years old IT professional and I was suffering from gradual teeth gap widening and misalignment due to aging factor. After my late thirties, a huge gap developed between my central incisors and somehow it started impacting my public speaking activities as my lips could not cover the protruding upper incisor teeth.  

Fortunately, I met Dr. Soham Mallick to whom I showed my 25 years old picture and asked, “Can my teeth become beautiful again like my teeth in this picture ?”. Dr. Soham’s emphatic and straight reply was “Yes” and it eliminated all my doubts and made me determined to get my Orthodontics treatment with him.

Getting my teeth re-aligned was certainly an arduous task to which Dr. Soham dealt very scientifically applying his previous experience understanding my teeth anatomy. One of his biggest feat is to complete my treatment without surgical interventions, which I initially presumed to be inevitable. Kudos to Dr. Soham’s diligent and perseverance endeavor to make my teeth back as it was when I was in 20s. 

I would strongly recommend Dr. Soham to all as he possess deep Orthodontics acumen and integrity who circumvent patient’s irrational medical expense making the treatment cost effective too.
